      "orgType": "COMPANY",
      "businessModel": "B2C",
      "description": "Independent third-party consumer products analytical testing laboratory founded circa 2000. Offers microbiological testing, instrumental analytical chemistry (HPLC, GC, ICP-MS, HPTLC, PCR), method development and validation, stability/shelf-life studies, heavy metals testing, cannabinoid profiling, allergen and PFAS analyses, environmental monitoring, and related services. Markets ISO/IEC 17025:2017 accreditation, FDA registration, DEA licensure and cGLP compliance. Operates a multi-site U.S. footprint (including Lehi, UT and other U.S. locations).",
